	- Forgot to add shortcut alias -d for --date.


0.006   2020-12-10  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Add argument 'date' for interoperability with
	  Health::BladderDiary::GenChart.


0.005   2020-12-10  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Allow more colors (0.5, 1.5, 2.5), tweak color output & column
	  name.

	- Add option: --yesterday-last-urination-entry (-y).

	- Add documentation.


0.004   2020-11-13  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: low

	- No functional changes.

	- [doc] Forgot to document vNUMBER shortcut.


0.003   2020-11-13  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- [ux] Allow specifying volume using v<NUM>, e.g. v100 (in addition
	  to volume=100 and 100ml).

	- Change formatting of time/hour column: 01-02.00 -> 01.00-02.00.


0.002   2020-11-12  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Some more convenience: allow entries as single lines if no blank lines
	  are found, shortcut for events drink (d) & urination (u or urin),
	  scrape u0..u10 for urgency=... and c0..c6 for color=clear/light
	  yellow/etc (using the 7-color-of-test-tubes urine color chart).

	- [test] Add some tests.


0.001   2020-11-11  Released-By: PERLANCAR

        - First release.
